data.description: This home is back on the market and move in ready! Upon entry of this beautiful home is a flex area that can be converted into another sitting area, den, office or formal dining room. The spacious kitchen wows with white cabinets, stainless steel gas appliances, upgraded cabinets, granite countertops and a walk-in pantry. A covered porch is just off the family room, inviting you to relax and spend Summer evenings in the backyard with friends and family. Relax in your primary bedroom upstairs featuring a grand vaulted ceiling, and enjoy your en-suite bath with dual vanity, walk-in shower with glass doors, and an oversized closet. The secondary bedrooms have plenty of space and sunlight, and share a double vanity in the secondary bathroom. This is the perfect place to call home. All this only minutes from SC-9, shopping, and within walking distance to elementary and middle schools. Model home in neighborhood is open. I would love to show you this beautiful home!
